column1: RIMNET DATASET STATISTICAL SUMMARY JANUARY - MARCH 2013
* The RIMNET monitor equipment at St Angelo (Enniskillen Airport) had to be removed from site on 10 January, prior to being relocated
to Thomas Town, Enniskillen on 5 February 2013.
The new site has been named Enniskillen and, for technical reasons, RIMNET data previously attributable to St Angelo will henceforth be held
under the new site name of Enniskillen.
